{"title":"沉思","authors":["袁圣梧"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":4,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉思"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袁圣梧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拾一片多彩的贝壳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻投于咆哮的海里；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等西天的晚霞消逝于微风的水面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伫立着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有谁知道我的怀念？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏着自己孤寂的影子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"默数着单调的跫音；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在月光的银辉铺满的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我徘徊着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有谁知道我的怀念？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"园中的玫瑰已不复清香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墙角口剩有蟋蟀的悲叹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看天上的星星又一颗失脚陨落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我凝视着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有谁知道我的怀念？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"失去的欢乐已无处寻找，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"止水般的心情已激不起波澜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听夜的木屐响过街心远了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我沉思着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有谁知道我的怀念？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伫立着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我徘徊着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我凝视着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我沉思着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又一个周末的黄昏去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有谁知道我的怀念？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔以上诗歌选自即将由人民文学出版社出版的《台湾诗歌选》〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}